title: Insaaf Ka Rakshak
subTitle: A sharpshooter falls in love with a girl who works in a cafe, but secretly uploads suicide videos. However, things take a turn when a cop looks for the person behind the videos.

title: Coolie Raja
subTitle: When a woman from a wealthy family falls in love with a porter, the couple tries to prove that their love is stronger than the differences in their social status.

title: Aaj Ka Naya Khiladi
subTitle: Siva unknowingly crosses a ruthless gangster while robbing the Home Minister's residence. Subsequently, the gangster kidnaps the Minister's daughter in retribution.

title: Anjaniputra
subTitle: A businessman saves a policeman from a group of thugs. As a result, he incurs the wrath of a ruthless local gangster who is also an assassin.

title: VIP 2 Lalkar
subTitle: A businesswoman is enraged when a civil engineer declines her job offer. With revenge on her mind, she decides to make his life troublesome.

title: Mawali Raaj
subTitle: In order to obtain a family of their own, two young children of two single parents devise a plan to bring them together.

title: Master Piece
subTitle: A young man falls in with the wrong crowd and strays from heroic deeds. However, an accidental encounter with danger forces him to change his ways.

title: Power Unlimited
subTitle: The home minister asks Tirupathi to impersonate the deceased ACP Baldev, his lookalike, to catch Ganguly, a dreaded gangster. After taking over his new role, he finds many startling revelations.

title: Saindhav
subTitle: A man with a traumatic past is compelled to encounter an crime boss so that he can rescue his daughter from a health problem.

title: Kabzaa - The Mafia Raaj
subTitle: Vijay Chandra, a determined police aspirant, battles a local MLA's corrupt efforts to seize his family's land. Joined by other wronged citizens, he takes a stand for justice and honor.

title: Kabzaa - The Mafia Raaj

title: Mera Farz
subTitle: Aalwar, a temple priest, leads a peaceful life until his mother and sister are murdered. In an attempt to take revenge, he adopts various disguises to teach a lesson to the perpetrators.

title: Jeene Do - Let Us Live
subTitle: An up-and-coming cyclist arrives in Mumbai for the final round of a championship. But his life takes a 180 degree turn when he discovers his family's painful past and sets out to avenge them.

title: Kacche Dhaagey
subTitle: Though Rani and Meet belong to different castes, they fall in love. However, when her family learns about their affair, they take a drastic step.

title: Bhumi Rakshak
subTitle: Two half-brothers peacefully co-exist with each other and their families. However, the return of an old enemy threatens the unity of the close-knit family.

title: Asli Fighter
subTitle: To free their imprisoned boss, a group of terrorists plan to bomb a flyover in Hyderabad. Amid all the chaos, unfortunately, a man and a woman get entangled in their plan.

title: Pichaikkaran 2
subTitle: Sathya is a poor man in search of his sister, who has been kidnapped by human traffickers. However, an illegal brain transplant puts him in the shoes of a billionaire named Vijay.

title: Theeran
subTitle: Theeran, a dedicated police officer, pays the price for his honesty and faces hardships when he tries to investigate the illegal activities conducted by a powerful gangster.

title: Madhagaja
subTitle: The wife of one of two rival dons sends her son to a distant land to shield him from their relentless feud. However, the son, raised as an orphan, eventually returns to the brutal world of violence.

title: Dashing CM Bharat
subTitle: Bharat, a graduate from Oxford, is forced to take up his father's position as the chief minister after his sudden death. He tries to reform the corrupt society but faces obstacles from his enemies.

title: My Boss Bajrangbali
subTitle: A corrupt politician kills Anji's parents and plans to demolish a temple. Later, Lord Hanuman takes human form to help Anji fight the politician.

title: My Boss Bajrangbali
subTitle: A corrupt politician kills Anji's parents and plans to demolish a temple. Later, Lord Hanuman takes human form to help Anji fight the politician.

title: The Fighter Mard No. 1
subTitle: An honest police officer, Prabhakaran, puts a notorious gangster, Easwaramoorthy, behind bars. When Easwaramoorthy learns of his identity, he decides to take revenge by targeting Prabhakaran's sister.

title: Sardar Saab
subTitle: Sardar Saab bravely stands up against the law and order bodies in his fight for justice for everyone around him. When he is killed, his son decides to avenge his death.

title: Action Blaster
subTitle: Anil Anto, a TV operator, moves to Kochi with his pregnant wife in order to start a new life. There, Anil crosses paths with Darvin, a gangster, post an unfortunate incident.

title: The Return Of Lion
subTitle: When a social worker dies, his son must not only avenge his death but also prove his innocence when the welfare fund money accumulated by his family goes missing.

title: Ek Aur Mrityu Pujan
subTitle: When the shadow of evil starts taking over the world, a warrior fights for good, as an avatar of Narasimha, a lion god, who is known for destroying evil.

title: Naa Saami Ranga
subTitle: A man gains great notoriety in his village for his unmatched strength and brutal nature, which makes him a target of antisocial elements with a ruthless agenda.

title: Rider
subTitle: As love blossoms between orphans Chinnu and Kitty, fate separates them as children. However, they grow up yearning to find each other.

title: Vijay Raghavan
subTitle: An honest IAS officer devotes his life to the upliftment of the youth in his locality. However, a corrupt businessman's ploy to poison these young minds compels him to challenge the criminal.

title: Sita Ram
subTitle: Ram, a young boy, lives in a monastery waiting for Sita to return and take care of him. However, Sita returns, years later, but with an ulterior motive.

title: Meri Taqat Mera Faisla
subTitle: A young man follows in his father's footsteps by working for the welfare of the people living in his district. However, a corrupt politician threatens to thwart his plans.
